---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Layout from "@layouts/index.astro";
import Header from "@components/header.svelte";
import HeroSecondary from "@components/hero_secondary.astro";
import john from "@images/john.jpg";
import graphic from "@images/graphic.svg";
---

<Layout title="About">
  <Header client:load />
  <HeroSecondary title="About" />
  <!-- main content wrapper applied padding -->
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div
      class="mx-auto grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 sm:gap-y-20 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-2 mt-28"
    >
      <Image
        src={john}
        alt="A picture of the owner, John"
        width="200"
        class="mx-auto"
      />
      <div class="lg:pr-8">
        <div class="lg:max-w-lg">
          <p class="text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">
            After spending a couple of years in the non-profit sector, I decided
            it was time to try something new. I had the impactful realization
            that I wanted to have my life's work be informed by my internal
            drive towards creativity and craftsmanship. After considering a
            bunch of options, I went to a coding bootcamp in 2015 and have not
            looked back since. While I am the owner and sole developer, I have a
            network of technical professionals I can reach out to, expanding the
            scope of the services I can offer to clients.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div
      class="mx-auto grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 sm:gap-y-20 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-2 mt-28"
    >
      <div class="lg:pr-8">
        <div class="lg:max-w-lg">
          <h3
            class="mt-2 text-pretty text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl"
          >
            Mission
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">
            To partner with clients to help solve their most pressing needs.
            Using an iterative, agile based work flow with quick feedback loops,
            I seek to solve for the present while keeping the future in mind.
            Usually, but not always, this involves the use of technology. Beyond
            any technical tasks, I seek to understand your business and your
            needs and present the simplest solution to you.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <Image src={graphic} alt="blended graphic" class="lg:mt-12" />
    </div>
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:mx-0 mt-28">
      <h3
        class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl"
      >
        Values
      </h3>
    </div>
    <dl
      class="mx-auto mt-6 grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-8 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:gap-x-16"
    >
      <div class="relative pl-9">
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke-width="1.5"
          stroke="currentColor"
          class="absolute left-1 top-1 h-5 w-5 text-way_blue"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            d="M20.25 8.511c.884.284 1.5 1.128 1.5 2.097v4.286c0 1.136-.847 2.1-1.98 2.193-.34.027-.68.052-1.02.072v3.091l-3-3c-1.354 0-2.694-.055-4.02-.163a2.115 2.115 0 0 1-.825-.242m9.345-8.334a2.126 2.126 0 0 0-.476-.095 48.64 48.64 0 0 0-8.048 0c-1.131.094-1.976 1.057-1.976 2.192v4.286c0 .837.46 1.58 1.155 1.951m9.345-8.334V6.637c0-1.621-1.152-3.026-2.76-3.235A48.455 48.455 0 0 0 11.25 3c-2.115 0-4.198.137-6.24.402-1.608.209-2.76 1.614-2.76 3.235v6.226c0 1.621 1.152 3.026 2.76 3.235.577.075 1.157.14 1.74.194V21l4.155-4.155"
          ></path>
        </svg>
        <dt>Communication</dt>
        <dd class="inline">
          I won't leave you guessing. I communicate early and often, making sure
          your project is on track.
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div class="relative pl-9">
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke-width="1.5"
          stroke="currentColor"
          class="absolute left-1 top-1 h-5 w-5 text-way_blue"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12c0 1.268-.63 2.39-1.593 3.068a3.745 3.745 0 0 1-1.043 3.296 3.745 3.745 0 0 1-3.296 1.043A3.745 3.745 0 0 1 12 21c-1.268 0-2.39-.63-3.068-1.593a3.746 3.746 0 0 1-3.296-1.043 3.745 3.745 0 0 1-1.043-3.296A3.745 3.745 0 0 1 3 12c0-1.268.63-2.39 1.593-3.068a3.745 3.745 0 0 1 1.043-3.296 3.746 3.746 0 0 1 3.296-1.043A3.746 3.746 0 0 1 12 3c1.268 0 2.39.63 3.068 1.593a3.746 3.746 0 0 1 3.296 1.043 3.746 3.746 0 0 1 1.043 3.296A3.745 3.745 0 0 1 21 12Z"
          ></path>
        </svg>
        <dt>Do it right</dt>
        <dd class="inline">
          You won't have to wonder what corners I'm cutting.
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div class="relative pl-9">
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke-width="1.5"
          stroke="currentColor"
          class="absolute left-1 top-1 h-5 w-5 text-way_blue"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            d="M21 8.25c0-2.485-2.099-4.5-4.688-4.5-1.935 0-3.597 1.126-4.312 2.733-.715-1.607-2.377-2.733-4.313-2.733C5.1 3.75 3 5.765 3 8.25c0 7.22 9 12 9 12s9-4.78 9-12Z"
          ></path>
        </svg>
        <dt>Honesty</dt>
        <dd class="inline">
          It's just easier for everybody if we tell the truth.
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div class="relative pl-9">
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke-width="1.5"
          stroke="currentColor"
          class="absolute left-1 top-1 h-5 w-5 text-way_blue"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            d="M4.26 10.147a60.438 60.438 0 0 0-.491 6.347A48.62 48.62 0 0 1 12 20.904a48.62 48.62 0 0 1 8.232-4.41 60.46 60.46 0 0 0-.491-6.347m-15.482 0a50.636 50.636 0 0 0-2.658-.813A59.906 59.906 0 0 1 12 3.493a59.903 59.903 0 0 1 10.399 5.84c-.896.248-1.783.52-2.658.814m-15.482 0A50.717 50.717 0 0 1 12 13.489a50.702 50.702 0 0 1 7.74-3.342M6.75 15a.75.75 0 1 0 0-1.5.75.75 0 0 0 0 1.5Zm0 0v-3.675A55.378 55.378 0 0 1 12 8.443m-7.007 11.55A5.981 5.981 0 0 0 6.75 15.75v-1.5"
          ></path>
        </svg>
        <dt>Always learning</dt>
        <dd class="inline">
          I care a lot about this craft and am continually expanding my
          knowledge and expertise to provide the best solutions available.
        </dd>
      </div>
    </dl>
  </div>
</Layout>
